pageContext.title: Irish Resources in the Humanities
pageContext.description_excerpt: Irish Resources in the Humanities was developed in 1999 by Dr. Susan Schreibman as a Gateway to sites on the World Wide Web that contain substantial content in the various disciplines of the humanities in the area of Irish Studies. As a rule, commercial sites are not linked.
pageContext.participants: Amit Kumar, Jason Rhody, Kevin Lynch, Susan Schreibman
